# Training & Competency Management System (TCMS)
A full-stack Angular + Node project designed for a 5-person team, showcasing real-world modular development and professional engineering practices.

---

## üéØ Project Goal
Build a Training & Competency Management System where employees can:
- Enroll in courses  
- Take quizzes  
- Track competencies & certifications  
- Receive expiry reminders  
- View analytics dashboards  

Employers see teamwork, architecture thinking, and production-quality structure.

---

# üöß Development Stages (Recommended Workflow)

## **Stage 1 ‚Äî Project Foundation**
- Initialize Angular workspace
- Initialize backend (Express/Nest)
- Set up shared folder structure
- Create database schema (SQL or NoSQL)
- Implement authentication (JWT + roles)
- Configure environment variables

**Deliverables:**  
Working login flow + basic project scaffolding.

---

## **Stage 2 ‚Äî Course Management Module**
- Course CRUD  
- Modules & lessons  
- File references (PDFs, videos, links)  
- Search & categorization  
- Angular UI for course listing + detail page  

**Deliverables:**  
Admin can create/edit courses. Employees can view and enroll.

---

## **Stage 3 ‚Äî Quiz & Assessment Module**
- Quiz creation  
- MCQ support  
- Quiz attempt submission  
- Auto-grading  
- Result history  

**Deliverables:**  
End-to-end quiz functionality.

---

## **Stage 4 ‚Äî Competency & Certification Module**
- Map competencies to job roles  
- Track user progress  
- Generate basic certificate PDF  
- Expiry notifications (cron job)  

**Deliverables:**  
Competency dashboard + PDF certificate download.

---

## **Stage 5 ‚Äî Analytics Dashboard + Final Polish**
- Charts: course enrollment, pass rates, competency completion  
- Export CSV  
- UI polishing with Angular Material  
- Add sample data & demo user accounts  
- Prepare README + demo script  

**Deliverables:**  
A polished, presentation-ready system.

---

# üèóÔ∏è Technology Stack
**Frontend:** Angular 17+, Angular Material, Chart.js / ngx-charts  
**Backend:** Node.js (Express or NestJS)  
**Database:** PostgreSQL / MySQL / MongoDB (choose 1 for the whole team)  
**Other:** JWT, Swagger, Docker (optional)

---

# üë• Team Modules (5 Members)

### **1. Auth & User Management (Member A)**
- Login, Register, Roles  
- JWT Auth Guard  
- User CRUD  

### **2. Courses Module (Member B)**
- Courses, Modules, Lessons  
- Filters + search  

### **3. Quiz Module (Member C)**
- Quiz builder  
- MCQ questions  
- User quiz attempts  

### **4. Competency Module (Member D)**
- Competency assignment  
- Certificates  
- Expiry reminders  

### **5. Analytics Module (Member E)**
- Reporting API  
- Charts + dashboards  
- CSV export  

---

# üì° API Endpoints (Summary Only)

### Auth
- POST /auth/login  
- POST /auth/register  
- GET /auth/profile  

### Courses
- GET /courses  
- POST /courses  
- GET /courses/:id  

### Quizzes
- GET /quizzes/course/:courseId  
- POST /quizzes/:id/attempt  

### Competencies
- GET /competencies  
- POST /competencies/assign  

### Analytics
- GET /analytics/overview  
- GET /analytics/courses  
- GET /analytics/competencies  

